title: The Teenagers- Reality Check 256kbps
description:
This is the sort of thing i would&#039;ve put up on Demonoid, so i thought I&#039;d share it on here seeing as most people seem to have &#039;fled&#039; to here.

This is the debut album from parisian (now based in London) trio The Teenagers, there was a lot of myspace/blogging buzz about them last year and hopefully 2008 will see them break into the mainstream. I was lucky enough to see them live about a year ago now, and would recommend seeing them on their upcoming UK tour.
